[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":405},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200929\u002F422561814\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200929\u002F422561814\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200929\u002F422561814\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200929\u002F422561814\u002F":382,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20200929\u002F422561814\u002F":391},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F09\u002F29\u002Flearn-hexo-16-minos-theme\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":365,"date":366,"description":18,"extension":367,"lang":368,"meta":369,"navigation":370,"path":371,"readingMinutes":372,"seo":373,"standalone":374,"stem":375,"tags":376,"tldr":379,"updated":379,"url":380,"__hash__":381},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F16-試著學-Hexo-主題篇-minos-主題.md","(16) 試著學 Hexo - 主題篇 - minos 主題","422561814",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":359},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,33,36,53,67,87,94,103,110,116,119,128,131,136,140,154,157,173,191,276,291,297,300,311,315,333,339,349,355],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來要來介紹另一個主題的安裝，也就是 minos 主題，這個主題在安裝上會稍微比較容易踩雷唷~",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"安裝-minos-主題","安裝 minos 主題",[16,24,25],{},"雖然安裝主題的過程基本上大同小異，但是還是有一些主題因為在設置上比較特殊，還是會踩雷唷~",[16,27,28],{},[29,30],"img",{"alt":31,"src":32},"踩雷，圖源：網路","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E8%B8%A9%E9%9B%B7.jpg",[16,34,35],{},"所以底下就直接提供主題的指令",[37,38,43],"pre",{"className":39,"code":40,"language":41,"meta":42,"style":42},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fppoffice\u002Fhexo-theme-minos.git themes\u002Fminos\n","cmd","",[44,45,46],"code",{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,48,51],"span",{"class":49,"line":50},"line",1,[47,52,40],{},[16,54,55,56,59,60,63,64],{},"這邊一樣的動作是到 ",[44,57,58],{},"hexo\u002F_config.yml"," 修改 ",[44,61,62],{},"theme"," 屬性成 ",[44,65,66],{},"minos",[37,68,72],{"className":69,"code":70,"language":71,"meta":42,"style":42},"language-yml shiki shiki-themes github-light github-light github-dark-high-contrast","theme: minos\n","yml",[44,73,74],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,75,76,79,83],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,77,62],{"class":78},"syv7_",[47,80,82],{"class":81},"s8XSl",": ",[47,84,86],{"class":85},"sWayO","minos\n",[16,88,89,90,93],{},"然後由於該主題的設置方式與 Hueman 相同，minos 只提供給你 _config.yml.example 並沒有 ",[44,91,92],{},"themes\u002F_config.yml","，因此這邊要輸入以下指令來拷貝一份出來",[37,95,97],{"className":39,"code":96,"language":41,"meta":42,"style":42},"cp themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml.example themes\u002Fminos\u002F_config.yml\n",[44,98,99],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,100,101],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,102,96],{},[16,104,105,106,109],{},"接下來你可能會直接輸入 ",[44,107,108],{},"hexo s"," 來模擬伺服器，但是這邊你一定會出現錯誤",[16,111,112],{},[29,113],{"alt":114,"src":115},"ERROR Package hexo-renderer-sass is not installed.","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-21%2011.43.11.png",[16,117,118],{},"這是因為 minos 主題還必須額外安裝一些套件才能正常運作，在這邊要輸入以下指令",[37,120,122],{"className":39,"code":121,"language":41,"meta":42,"style":42},"npm install --save hexo-renderer-sass cheerio\n",[44,123,124],{"__ignoreMap":42},[47,125,126],{"class":49,"line":50},[47,127,121],{},[16,129,130],{},"此時才能夠正常運作模擬伺服器唷",[16,132,133],{},[29,134],{"alt":66,"src":135},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-08-21%2012.03.07.png",[12,137,139],{"id":138},"minos-設置檔案","minos 設置檔案",[16,141,142,143,146,147,149,150,153],{},"minos 也是相對比較短，因此這邊就不再介紹，主要會介紹的地方是修改語言的部分，minos 會基於你的 ",[44,144,145],{},"theme\u002F_config.yml"," 來切換語系，因此這邊如果你希望畫面呈現的是繁體中文，那麼就要將原本的 ",[44,148,145],{}," 修改成 ",[44,151,152],{},"theme\u002F_config.zh-tw.yml","。",[16,155,156],{},"當然 minos 還有一個特色就是支援多國語系，因此你可以依照相關語系建立底下檔案依序輸入以下指令建立多國語系檔案",[37,158,160],{"classN